  "text": "Since the original theorem by Arrow [CITATION_1] , many efforts have been made to weaken its conditions. In fact, both the domain and the codomain of a social welfare function have been the subject of more relaxed assumptions in several Arrow-like impossibility theorems. Here we review some of them and we relate them to our work.",
